task.persona: A younger tennis player with quick reflexes working their way up through the ranks

instruction.level1: Create an event on May 20th for a tennis practice session at 3 PM
instruction.level2: Create an event on May 20th at 3 PM for a tennis practice session.
instruction.level3: Create an event titled 'Tennis Practice Session' on May 20th, 2026, at 3 PM.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event.
Select 'Event' from the menu to start creating a new event.
Fill in the event title with 'Tennis Practice Session'
Open the date and time editor to change the event date and time.
Fill in the start date with 'Tuesday, May 20'
Fill in the start time with '3:00 PM' for the event.
Click the Save button to finalize the event creation.
